    "ASR ′ represents ASR post-application of our defense pipeline with default settings.",
    "Suffixes were tailored to each attacked model by generating them using the appropriate AmpleGCG or AmpleGCG-plus model as described in Kumar et al. [22].",
    "(+) indicates the fact that suffixes were generated using the updated -plus variant of AmpleGCG.",
    "ASR is evaluated via HarmBench-cls [25].",
    "(a) Evaluated on the full dataset, using the standard method described in Kumar et al. [22]."
